 pve-manager (9.2.4) trixie; urgency=medium
 
   * fix #4130: external metric server: keep node status updates flowing when a
     TCP metric server is unreachable. A failed connection previously raised an
     unhandled exception that aborted the whole node status update, so storage
     and guest status indicators in the UI eventually turned gray.
 
